Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你的到来  昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小帆帆的父亲  三泽风雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方面是为了感谢你做小帆帆的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外今天是个特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（祝  三泽真帆&长谷川昴  订婚派对）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你们  小帆帆  昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订…订婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帆  这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿昴要订婚吗  我都不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说到订婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是可以放进关东煮  还可以沾味噌吃的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是蒟蒻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小帆帆  我是不是搞错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  你搞错了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴是大家的阿昴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要订婚的话大家要一起订婚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小帆帆说到昴君的事就非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你们的关系已经非比寻常了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系非比寻常…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  先不说订婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的很想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  跟小帆帆说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个有为的好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的话  我就可以放心把小帆帆托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:01:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是都说了嘛  阿昴是最棒的教练了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  哥哥最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你比看上去要更可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天突然邀请你来  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为给你添的麻烦做些补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么我能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您言重了  补偿什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必客气  尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专用的篮球场地也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NBA的现场观赛之旅也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然把整支梦之队请来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸真大方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长谷川哥哥  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的好意我很感激  但是做到那种地步实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…风雅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…ForM不是真帆爸爸的牌子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉各种不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那种事  这个参加资格和特别规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加资格  小学生5人队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中禁止换人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个规则的话  我们和智花她们都能参加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报仇的机会这么快就来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧  真帆大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们绝对不会输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  想赢过智花她们可不是那么简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们变强的同时他们也在变强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样也要赢  绝对要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多说无益  快点开始练习吧  没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说我们也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿  来这边练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  全员集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以大赛为目标  从今天起练习特别课目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别课目？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大赛还挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫  说不定很快就能见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你憧憬的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜喵  累死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的练习课目超难耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是长谷川哥哥为大赛制定的特别课目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很辛苦  但是加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这么轻易就趴下的话  会输给小花的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年级的各位一定也在拼命练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙  我们也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始做100次仰卧起坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴哥哥说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要相信至今为止所做过的努力就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  既然是哥哥说的  日向也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们带到这一步的正是长谷川哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了原本不能参加正式比赛的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备了这么棒的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要加油  一定要获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极…极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  跑不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在跑步  这就是特别课目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种事真的能赢纱季她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是教练生气了才让我们做这种强人所难的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪雅美自己开始投篮练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才是  两个人自顾自地进行传球练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得美美和花月一个人练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静  冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别参加这次大赛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为参赛资格是小学生五人的「队伍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一盘散沙  这样真的能称作「队伍」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算参赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照现在的样子还是会输给六年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光做这种跑步练习  真的能赢过纱季她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  什么都不做的话绝对赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「队伍」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得很直白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不甘心  但是没办法反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的意见  一语中的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想赢过姐姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止需要体力和技术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得团队合作也是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的方面都还不足  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs15\pos(269,324)}Show  you  guts  cool  say  what
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学生最棒了  哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能去做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教  教练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按照教练说的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能赢过六年级生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我无法保证  但是有办法与她们拼一拼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为你们指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拼命啊  不论是那些孩子还是葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  不得不承认实力的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆冷才有意思  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我再做一次挑战宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你瞧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野猪的战斗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我在这里宣布迷你篮球大赛开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来宣布让大家久等的抽签结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山原兔子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是风雅先生的兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该不该看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  看起来是个很有趣的分组呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够顺利获胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个队伍会在准决赛对决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱季  我们想说的只有一句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  如果我们今天赢了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就会成为正式的篮球部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不反对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我们赢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一段时间里  你们要当我们的助手陪我们练习如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想把我们当做奴隶随意使唤么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正只要我们赢了就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如雅美所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正赢的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心被反咬一口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  明明只是笨蛋真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六年级队赢的话  就能成为10人的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能够参加正式比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是智花她们一起想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对哪个队伍来说  有个练习对手会更好些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  她们输掉的话会不会乖乖遵从呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了  昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻奈佳学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把砚谷的队伍也带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  手术成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我应该发过短信给小葵的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让昴吃一惊  所以保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还没有完全痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也在顺利地恢复当中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然打篮球真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砚谷参加的话  那么未有她们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这次主力们缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是我自夸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队的替补里面也聚集着许多精英
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩是我们值得期待的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫都大路绫  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫她原本是体操部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如你们所见  身体突然长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就立刻让她加入篮球部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  难得你邀请我参加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我篮球打得很差
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  难道你是爱莉同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  队里的伙伴告诉我  一定要和你聊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在慧心还有比我更高的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然长高了  一定吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉周围的世界好像从身边逃走一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后害怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢体操
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是长高之后  就没法好好顺利完成动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就变成了累赘  想要试着挑战篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这边也变成了累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后渐渐失去信心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次打篮球的时候  也十分差劲  是别人的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也还是完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉同学也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是在球场上身高却一次次帮助了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了只有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小绫也一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴能和爱莉同学说上话  非常  非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  希望能够再和小绫聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  爱莉好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉真的成长成了不起的孩子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在慧心学园6年级队与和田小学篮球社的比赛即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请两只队伍到A球场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么昴君  我在决赛等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还没碰面就输了的话  我可不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我要说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  大家出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和往常一样  将之前的训练全部展现出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的话一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照我们的节奏一定能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿智  纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有靠小聪明  而是单纯的体力决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用速度来一决胜负么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦  真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间还很充足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是场精彩的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打到这里基本不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  6年级处于下风？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢  我也以为不相上下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始在意分差了么  投篮命中率开始下降了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  昴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想太多的话  脚步不就停下来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵才是  像只野猪一样冲太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行  她们完全跟不上我们的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全能够看清对方的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿还能够跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习成果发挥出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次输了那么多  但这次却是我们领先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和葵的作战完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  大家表现的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教练  我的投篮怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的断球很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习的效果都展现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去能够赢过纱季她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  要是那边也没有改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这和对方的策略无关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只用打我们的篮球  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  这是最简单  也是最困难的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在的大家能够办到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己  然后相信大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  下半场了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,———————ED———————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5年级队变得越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也必须要提高自己作为控球后卫的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个回转寿司来锻炼动态视力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好晕…
